docs {
  ## List Report Templates
  แสดงรายการแม่แบบรายงานทั้งหมด

  Retrieve all active report templates.


  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": [
      {
        "id": "uuid",
        "name": "Stock Report",
        "report_group": "inventory",
        "is_active": true
      }
    ],
    "paginate": {
      "total": 100,
      "page": 1,
      "perpage": 10,
      "pages": 10
    },
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}

